This paper deals with low-rank tensor factorization for visual data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses noise modelling, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which may fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
